headline: Buy This Ultra-Safe High-Yield Dividend King Stock for Reliable Passive Income
summary: Kenvue (NYSE: KVUE) stock is down since completing its spin-off from Johnson & Johnson (NYSE: JNJ) in August 2023.  Kenvue is a stable stalwart with a growing dividend.  Here's why the future is bright for Kenvue and why the high-yield dividend stock is worth a closer look for risk-averse investors looking to boost their passive income stream.
